ygData.messageBody:
Salutations All!

Hey, I'm just curious as to what are the best and
worst classes and races to play in EQ? Your personal
favorites. As a relative newcomer to the game I would
be especially interested in what some of you who have
been playing the game for a while think on that topic
as I'm trying to decide on creating another character
and cant make up my mind.

My principal 20th lvl character is Wood Elf Ranger
I also have a lvl one Iksar Shadow Knight but I've
done nothing with them and may drop them.
Finally, I have a lvl 2 half elf bard. This toon was
actually made a long time ago when I first bought EQ
but could not get it to run properly. Oddly when I
finally did get it to work I found her still there as
first lvl. Anyway, any comments are appreciated.

Hugs
:o)
Bran
